ActDirector of Public Prosecutions Act
PrecisAuthorization of KATHLEEN ROUSSEL of Ottawa, Ontario, Deputy Director of Public Prosecutions, to act as Director of Public Prosecutions, during pleasure, to fill a vacancy in that office for the period beginning on March 6, 2017 and ending on June 20, 2017, or until a Director of Public Prosecutions is appointed, whichever occurs first.
